{"tid":1374090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢原本企街站崗 點知最後去咗前線 然後喊醒咗","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:52:27.000Z","uid":181257,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa45340b66340460767a94bdcc68e2f77875f43","tid":1374090,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"岩岩發咗個好奇怪嘅夢<br />\n<br />\n8點幾喺Yoho外圍防守 以防有白衫出動攻擊市民<br />\n點知聽到西鐵站要人 就行咗過去<br />\n去到西鐵站中間，G出口天橋無啦啦有催淚彈掉咗上黎<br />\n前線朋友上前撲滅，呢個時候，yoho又傳有狗衝入黎，好似想玩圍補，氣氛十分緊張<br />\n<br />\n呢次係我第一次發夢上前線，眼見好多朋友仲瘦過我，年紀好細，雖然淨係可以望到佢哋對眼，睇得出每個都好累又擔心，但係個眼神十分堅定，狗想上黎，前面嘅人縮一縮，又衝番上前。<br />\n<br />\n有人喺咁勸佢哋走走，佢話：要後無gear嘅後排上晒車，佢哋先走，而家佢哋buy緊time。我聽到，眼淚不禁流落黎，點解要年輕人承受呢一切，原諒我有包袱唔敢走上前，我只可以做嘅，係盡最大努力勸後排唔知想點嘅人上月台，每次前排大叫，我哋就往後退叫其他人慢慢行唔好急。<br />\n<br />\n喺四面受敵嘅情況下，我見到有手足見人無頭盔即刻遞個頭盔俾佢，自己擔心但更會擔心同伴安全，first Aid 幫人做急救時會手拖手圍圈等佢哋有足夠位置工作。<br />\n<br />\n香港年輕人，點解你哋可以噉團結，噉可愛，我好愛你哋<br />\n無論今次結果係點，我好自豪噉講 我係香港人，我更自豪有幸同你哋一齊發夢，我愛你，真係好愛<br />\n<br />\n一路打篇野一路喊，我需要小小時間平復，今晚一齊早啲休息，明天再發場好夢。"},{"pid":"5038492be7bc31bff38a861e6f87a3a8469d5ee3","tid":1374090,"uid":273708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:16:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"c43339c5e2c3c421a96970d704356251db4f7807","tid":1374090,"uid":201649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"8a42966ed484b5bd8e9fcf6b44634e048d19d5a3","tid":1374090,"uid":183674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:17:49.000Z","msg":"休息好啲"},{"pid":"43b412d35c1f592016981010b79574b1e08a5ad6","tid":1374090,"uid":216088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:17:50.000Z","msg":"We are HongKongers"},{"pid":"f48946763ae4d0ae9874eff5be8a9a40519ae678","tid":1374090,"uid":29560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:17:50.000Z","msg":"加油巴打<br />\n你已經做得好好"},{"pid":"15ac2d08aa81327c7066b1823851a16df92c8ca7","tid":1374090,"uid":5813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"13070a437ef4959bd3ed7a1159808723655c9be5","tid":1374090,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f30a963b97d7c8c1c7cce8abebeef08e5b70cb3","tid":1374090,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"好生休養 準備明天"},{"pid":"4becc5caf336b9742f9c7d228b4abe6be45a955d","tid":1374090,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fe08b455177928a2a7f63b6a6af96ab849374b","tid":1374090,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:20:35.000Z","msg":"多謝你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff958a7b63e495224b3028b44a368a68b36141b","tid":1374090,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8528921c3da2b85631363b6b26a0a5daa917101","tid":1374090,"uid":275128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"6a095971422bf9436ca9bd2b29d3bcfc6c438839","tid":1374090,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:35:31.000Z","msg":"我相信 終有一日 我哋唔洗夢中相見"},{"pid":"e203bad804cb5390f7a40f735d794a202abfd87f","tid":1374090,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0542efd1b714a20d3